The paper discusses the behavior of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper specifically focuses on visualizing the decision function of the model and the data set in two dimensions, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV).
